ecedence, ensuring runtime permissions respect user configuration and seeded defaults.&#10;- Created tables for `docperm` and `custom_docperm` to align with extended merging behavior.&#10;- Updated `.idea` project files to reflect new module additions.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783583306744</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00003\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00003\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783583306744</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00004\" summary=\"Add email connectivity module and extend permission merging logic&#10;&#10;- Introduced a new `crates/email` module for handling SMTP/IMAP connectivity, configuration, and testing. Includes `test_email_settings`, `send_email`, and `fetch_inbox` methods for email operations.&#10;- Extended the PermissionEngine to merge `docperm`, `__kiff_docperm`, and `custom_docperm` permissions with precedence, ensuring runtime permissions respect user configuration and seeded defaults.&#10;- Created tables for `docperm` and `custom_docperm` to align with extended merging behavior.&#10;- Updated `.idea` project files to reflect new module additions.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783583338908</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00004\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00004\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783583338908</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00005\" summary=\"Add `audit_ready` app for server token management&#10;&#10;Introduced the `audit_ready` app for managing infrastructure server tokens, including UI, HTTP handlers, and backend processes. Updated `sync_rust_apps.py` to support case-insensitive app directory resolution and adjusted project files accordingly.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783701589796</created>\n      