 <task id=\"LOCAL-00027\" summary=\"Add detailed debug logging for OAuth provider resolution and Social Login Key matching steps\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783937006043</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00027\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00027\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783937006043</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00028\" summary=\"Add `restrict_to_domain` field to Doctype and enhance workspace child-table handling\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783946699298</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00028\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00028\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783946699298</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00029\" summary=\"Add support for page fixtures and extend infrastructure UI&#10;&#10;Introduced handling for page fixtures in `sync_all()` to enable better alignment with permission checks and native pages. Updated infrastructure workspace and frontend screens to include new shortcuts and links, such as &quot;Server Token Generator&quot; and &quot;SEBRUS::OPS&quot; pages. Enhanced database handling for pages with additional fields like `restrict_to_domain`.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783952296620</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00029\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00029\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783952296620</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00030\" summary=\"Update log engine data files and index metadata&#10;&#10;Refreshed log entries in `wal.ndjson`, updated `.managed.json` with new index files, and modified `meta.json` to include new segments.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783966205438</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00030\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00030\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783966205438</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00031\" summary=\"Add workspace redirects and enhance fleet UI filtering&#10;&#10;Introduced redirects for custom workspace pages in Rust runtime to align with new URL structure. Enhanced fleet UI with status-based filtering and visibility counts, improving user experience in Ops Portal. Updated log engine data files and index metadata to reflect recent changes in logs and segments.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1783971205448</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00031\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00031\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1783971205448</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00032\" summary=\"Implement batch processing of logs and optimize vulnerability scans.&#10;&#10;Add batch ingestion to reduce write overhead for high-frequency logs. Optimize vulnerability scans by batching database writes, skipping unchanged servers, and enhancing OSV concurrency limits. Also introduce telemetry and heartbeat caching for improved performance.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784049011223</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00032\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00032\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784049011223</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00033\" summary=\"Implement batch processing of logs and optimize vulnerability scans.&#10;&#10;Add batch ingestion to reduce write overhead for high-frequency logs. Optimize vulnerability scans by batching database writes, skipping unchanged servers, and enhancing OSV concurrency limits. Also introduce telemetry and heartbeat caching for improved performance.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784049058101</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00033\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00033\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784049058101</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00034\" summary=\"Add in-memory caches for telemetry and job handling.&#10;&#10;Introduced RAM-based caches for patch jobs, software inventories, and log staging to reduce SQLite contention and enhance system responsiveness. Updated APIs and the log engine to leverage these caches for high-frequency tasks, ensuring consistent, real-time performance while persisting data asynchronously.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784060571483</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00034\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00034\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784060571483</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00035\" summary=\"Refactor and optimize batch processing in core components&#10;&#10;Revised batch processing logic across multiple modules to reduce write contention and improve performance. Introduced chunked operations, environment-variable-driven configurations, and logic to cap resource usage dynamically, ensuring better scalability under heavy loads.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784095629273</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00035\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00035\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784095629273</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00036\" summary=\"Refactor code for improved readability and formatting.&#10;&#10;Enhanced code readability by reformatting multi-line constructs such as match arms, function calls, and array definitions. Applied consistent indentation and alignment to enhance maintainability and prepare for future contributions.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784102007028</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00036\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00036\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784102007028</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00037\" summary=\"Optimize database pool management and enhance vulnerability data handling.&#10;&#10;Added self-healing mechanisms for wedged SQLite pools to prevent data corruption and improve reliability. Introduced shared fetch caches and payload capping for vulnerability alerts in the frontend to enhance performance and reduce server load.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784199823012</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00037\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00037\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784199823012</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00038\" summary=\"Remove auto-generated server token logic&#10;&#10;Eliminated legacy code for auto-creating tokens during server or client insertion, reinforcing explicit token generation via the API for better security and consistency. Updated related tests and SQL filtering, and added new token-related unit tests for validation.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784205192863</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00038\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00038\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784205192863</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00039\" summary=\"Add tunnel agent reconnection logic to Ops Portal&#10;&#10;Introduced an automatic reconnection mechanism that waits for the tunnel agent to come online before establishing a WebSocket connection. Enhanced user feedback with updated status indicators and streamlined session cleanup to handle reconnection scenarios effectively.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784206769489</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00039\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00039\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784206769489</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00040\" summary=\"Add diagnostics for agent connection attempts in Ops Portal&#10;&#10;Extended server response to include details on the most recent agent connection attempt when no agent is connected. Added support for tracking connection attempt timestamps, success status, and error messages in `BrokerState`. Updated the frontend to display this information for better debugging and user feedback.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784208690979</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00040\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00040\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784208690979</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00041\" summary=\"&quot;Implement WebSocket keepalive ping for idle timeout prevention&#10;&#10;Added a periodic keepalive ping mechanism to maintain active WebSocket connections by preventing idle timeouts. Adjusted the connection interval and idle task management to ensure dead connections are reaped while live connections remain responsive. Updated related documentation to explain the new behavior.&quot;\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784231598025</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00041\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00041\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784231598025</updated>\n    </task>\n    <task id=\"LOCAL-00042\" summary=\"Add per-server activity cache and node-level network/process views&#10;&#10;Introduced an in-memory cache for per-server process and network activity to enable real-time data retrieval. Enhanced the frontend with live network monitoring and process inspection for individual nodes, including efficient renders for large data sets and dynamic view updates.\">\n      <option name=\"closed\" value=\"true\" />\n      <created>1784300910935</created>\n      <option name=\"number\" value=\"00042\" />\n      <option name=\"presentableId\" value=\"LOCAL-00042\" />\n      <option name=\"project\" value=\"LOCAL\" />\n      <updated>1784300910935</updated>\n    </task>\n    <option name=\"localTasksCounter\" value=\"43\" />\n    <servers />\n  </component>\n  <component name=\"TypeScriptGeneratedFilesManager\">\n    <option name=\"version\" value=\"3\" />\n  </component>\n  <component name=\"UnknownFeatures\">\n    <option featureType=\"com.intellij.fileTypeFactory\" implementationName=\"*.py\" />\n  </component>\n  <component name=\"VcsManagerConfiguration\">\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Improve logging and error handling for initialization paths&#10;&#10;Enhanced initialization logic for the crash-durable log engine in Rust and added comprehensive fallback mechanisms for building redirect_uri in Python. Improved debug logging in both cases to aid troubleshooting and clarify error contexts.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Refactor OAuth `redirect_uri` logic for better request context handling&#10;&#10;Simplified the construction of `redirect_uri` by prioritizing request headers and context over fallback mechanisms. Ensured compatibility with Microsoft Entra ID by enforcing absolute URI requirements. Streamlined error handling for edge cases.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Enhance OAuth `redirect_uri` handling with improved fallback logic and detailed debug logging\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Refactor OAuth provider mapping and enhance Microsoft tenant configuration&#10;&#10;Streamlined the logic for resolving OAuth provider keys and Social Login Keys. Added support to dynamically configure tenant-specific Microsoft OAuth endpoints using tenant IDs from environment or config. Improved compatibility by rewriting `/common/` endpoints to tenant-specific URLs.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add enhanced logging and tenant-specific handling for OAuth providers&#10;&#10;Improved debug and warning logs for OAuth provider flows. Added logic to rewrite `/common/` Microsoft OAuth endpoints to tenant-specific URLs. Enhanced flow configuration to ensure compatibility and accuracy of authorization and token exchange mechanisms.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add detailed debug logging for OAuth provider resolution and Social Login Key matching steps\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add `restrict_to_domain` field to Doctype and enhance workspace child-table handling\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add support for page fixtures and extend infrastructure UI&#10;&#10;Introduced handling for page fixtures in `sync_all()` to enable better alignment with permission checks and native pages. Updated infrastructure workspace and frontend screens to include new shortcuts and links, such as &quot;Server Token Generator&quot; and &quot;SEBRUS::OPS&quot; pages. Enhanced database handling for pages with additional fields like `restrict_to_domain`.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Update log engine data files and index metadata&#10;&#10;Refreshed log entries in `wal.ndjson`, updated `.managed.json` with new index files, and modified `meta.json` to include new segments.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add workspace redirects and enhance fleet UI filtering&#10;&#10;Introduced redirects for custom workspace pages in Rust runtime to align with new URL structure. Enhanced fleet UI with status-based filtering and visibility counts, improving user experience in Ops Portal. Updated log engine data files and index metadata to reflect recent changes in logs and segments.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Implement batch processing of logs and optimize vulnerability scans.&#10;&#10;Add batch ingestion to reduce write overhead for high-frequency logs. Optimize vulnerability scans by batching database writes, skipping unchanged servers, and enhancing OSV concurrency limits. Also introduce telemetry and heartbeat caching for improved performance.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add real-time RAM caching for log ingestion and fleet status.&#10;&#10;Introduced an in-memory staging buffer for log records to enhance ingestion performance by reducing disk writes. Extended fleet status and patch job handling to leverage RAM caches for real-time updates, minimizing SQLite queries and improving responsiveness across both APIs and the UI.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add in-memory caches for telemetry and job handling.&#10;&#10;Introduced RAM-based caches for patch jobs, software inventories, and log staging to reduce SQLite contention and enhance system responsiveness. Updated APIs and the log engine to leverage these caches for high-frequency tasks, ensuring consistent, real-time performance while persisting data asynchronously.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add dynamic configuration and improve batching efficiency&#10;&#10;Introduce environment variable-based overrides for various parameters, such as log engine heap size, max SQLite connections, batch sizes, and intervals, to enhance configurability. Refactor existing bulk operations and background tasks to process in chunks, reducing contention and improving performance. Additionally, adjust defaults for more resource-efficient operation on constrained systems.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Refactor and optimize batch processing in core components&#10;&#10;Revised batch processing logic across multiple modules to reduce write contention and improve performance. Introduced chunked operations, environment-variable-driven configurations, and logic to cap resource usage dynamically, ensuring better scalability under heavy loads.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Refactor code for improved readability and formatting.&#10;&#10;Enhanced code readability by reformatting multi-line constructs such as match arms, function calls, and array definitions. Applied consistent indentation and alignment to enhance maintainability and prepare for future contributions.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Optimize database pool management and enhance vulnerability data handling.&#10;&#10;Added self-healing mechanisms for wedged SQLite pools to prevent data corruption and improve reliability. Introduced shared fetch caches and payload capping for vulnerability alerts in the frontend to enhance performance and reduce server load.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Remove auto-generated server token logic&#10;&#10;Eliminated legacy code for auto-creating tokens during server or client insertion, reinforcing explicit token generation via the API for better security and consistency. Updated related tests and SQL filtering, and added new token-related unit tests for validation.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add tunnel agent wait loop for remote shell connections&#10;&#10;Introduced automatic retries for connecting to disconnected tunnel agents. Updated shell status display to differentiate between &quot;CONNECTING&quot; and &quot;WAITING FOR AGENT&quot; states. Refactored tunnel connection logic for improved maintainability.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add tunnel agent reconnection logic to Ops Portal&#10;&#10;Introduced an automatic reconnection mechanism that waits for the tunnel agent to come online before establishing a WebSocket connection. Enhanced user feedback with updated status indicators and streamlined session cleanup to handle reconnection scenarios effectively.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add diagnostic tracking for agent connection attempts&#10;&#10;Introduced `AgentAttempt` to track and surface diagnostic details about agent connection attempts, aiding server admins in debugging connection issues. Updated Ops Portal to display the last attempt's status and message. Enhanced broker logic to record both successful and failed attempts, with relevant details shared in API responses.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add diagnostics for agent connection attempts in Ops Portal&#10;&#10;Extended server response to include details on the most recent agent connection attempt when no agent is connected. Added support for tracking connection attempt timestamps, success status, and error messages in `BrokerState`. Updated the frontend to display this information for better debugging and user feedback.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"&quot;Implement WebSocket keepalive ping for idle timeout prevention&#10;&#10;Added a periodic keepalive ping mechanism to maintain active WebSocket connections by preventing idle timeouts. Adjusted the connection interval and idle task management to ensure dead connections are reaped while live connections remain responsive. Updated related documentation to explain the new behavior.&quot;\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add per-server activity cache and node-level network/process views&#10;&#10;Introduced an in-memory cache for per-server process and network activity to enable real-time data retrieval. Enhanced the frontend with live network monitoring and process inspection for individual nodes, including efficient renders for large data sets and dynamic view updates.\" />\n    <MESSAGE value=\"Add toggle for node processes visibility in ops portal&#10;&#10;Introduced a toggle button to show/hide the node processes block in the node panel, enhancing session-level user preferences. Updated related CSS for a smaller button size and adjusted the HTML structure to accommodate visibility states. Runtime log file was extended, and a minor &quot;opstamp&quot; value change was made in the meta.json file.\" />\n    <option name=\"LAST_COMMIT_MESSAGE\" value=\"Add toggle for node processes visibility in ops portal&#10;&#10;Introduced a toggle button to show/hide the node processes block in the node panel, enhancing session-level user preferences. Updated related CSS for a smaller button size and adjusted the HTML structure to accommodate visibility states. Runtime log file was extended, and a minor &quot;opstamp&quot; value change was made in the meta.json file.\" />\n  </component>\n</project>
